# TASK MANAGER (C++)

The project consists in a task manager developed in C++ to practice Object Oriented Programming, data structure and file persistence.

## Features

- Create tasks
- List all tasks
- Update task status
- Remove tasks
- Set task priority (low, medium, high)
- Data persistence using files

---

